&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Oversight:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify risks and inefficiencies in financial processes, taking corrective action and translating complex data into actionable insights for leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Managerial Scope:&lt;/strong&gt; Build, mentor, and recruit a high-performing accounting team, fostering a culture of ownership, precision, and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
